    {
      "parameters": {
        "prompt": "={{ $json.task_history }}\n\n---\nYou are a behavioral data scientist AI for LifeSyncPro. Analyze the user's 3-week task history above. Look for patterns in when tasks are 'completed' vs 'missed' based on their 'scheduled_start' times.\n\nIdentify sleep windows, peak productivity hours, times they ignore tasks, burnout limits, and weekly recurring unavailable blocks.\n\nOutput STRICTLY a raw JSON object (no markdown, no backticks, no explanations) with exactly these keys:\n{\n  \"inferred_sleep_window\": \"e.g. 00:00-08:00\",\n  \"peak_productivity_windows\": \"e.g. 10:00-12:00, 14:00-16:00\",\n  \"high_ignore_probability_windows\": \"e.g. 18:00-20:00\",\n  \"daily_burnout_threshold\": 5,\n  \"weekly_hard_blocks\": \"e.g. Friday 13:00-14:00\"\n}"
      },
      "id": "27d84562-3cb4-4cb6-8acc-a6d31bfc3164",
      "name": "Basic LLM Chain",
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.chainLlm",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        608,
        -16
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "5f59c415-3b98-4469-9044-9bc822e34634",
      "name": "Google Gemini Chat Model",
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.lmChatGoogleGemini",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        608,
        192
      ],
      "credentials": {
        "googlePalmApi": {
          "id": "YoE88NOLwRInHR5L",
          "name": "Google Gemini(PaLM) Api account"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const text = $input.first().json.text;\n\n// Dynamically reach back and grab the user_id from the first task we fetched!\nconst fetchedData = $('Fetch Last 21 Days').first().json;\nconst dynamicUserId = fetchedData.user_id;\n\nlet parsed;\ntry {\n  // Clean markdown if Gemini accidentally adds it\n  const cleanText = text.replace(/```json/g, '').replace(/```/g, '').trim();\n  parsed = JSON.parse(cleanText);\n} catch (error) {\n  throw new Error(\"Failed to parse Gemini output as JSON: \" + text);\n}\n\nreturn {\n  json: {\n    user_id: dynamicUserId,\n    inferred_sleep_window: parsed.inferred_sleep_window,\n    peak_productivity_windows: parsed.peak_productivity_windows,\n    high_ignore_probability_windows: parsed.high_ignore_probability_windows,\n    daily_burnout_threshold: parsed.daily_burnout_threshold,\n    weekly_hard_blocks: parsed.weekly_hard_blocks\n  }\n};"
      },
      "id": "d0e8ee0d-bc5a-4ddf-a9ac-dd56b9b13d93",
      "name": "Parse JSON & Attach ID",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
